<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA513_02_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema513_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema513_02_ih_0001">
      <section class="title group">
        <h2 lang="y"><span class="pink">[1~3]</span> 상자의 수와 초콜릿의 수 사이의 대응 관계를 알아보려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="img_box mt_20">
        <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA513_02_IH/0001_img.png" alt="" />
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_pink" lang="y">표를 완성해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box">
          <div class="table_wrap">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">상자의 수(개)</th>
                  <td scope="col">1</td>
                  <td scope="col">2</td>
                  <td scope="col">3</td>
                  <td scope="col">4</td>
                  <td scope="col">...</td>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">초콜릿의 수(개)</th>
                  <td>3</td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>...</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">상자가 1개, 2개, 3개, 4개, ...일 때, 초콜릿은 3개, 6개, 9개, 12개, ...입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
